title: New: Billie Black – Going Under
body:
Fairly sure I remember this track being part of **Billie Black’s** set supporting Nao at Electrowerkz last year, and really vibing to it at the time.

Pretty different to anything she’s done before, and definitely starting to really carve out a niche for herself, it’s well worth a listen. The first track lifted from a new EP, out 25 Mayl check out _Going Under_ below.
